title: Eclipse fills (Portia Prinz, Steed, Zorro)
description:
The ECUP ignores the primary condition of its parole and returns to old stomping grounds, with an Eclipse Fill!

Enclosed, you will find two complete series and a one-shot:

Portia Prinz of the Glamazons 1-6 - B&W series written and illustrated by Richard Howell.

Steed and Mrs. Peel 1-3 - Early work from Grant Morrison and Ian Gibson! (This was recently reprinted over 6 issues by Boom! Studios)

Zorro in Old California - English translation of strips written by Jean-Marie Nadaud and cleanly-illustrated by Carlo Marcello.

Giggity giggity to the creative teams and scanners! Purloin it, provide it!
